$ sudo docker pull jenkins/jenkins:lts
$ sudo docker run -p 8080:8080 -p 50000:50000 -v jenkins_home:/var/jenkins_home jenkins/jenkins:lts
Grab the initial admin pass from the startup logs.
Browse to http://<IP>:8080
Login, choose some plugins. Create an admin user.
Click Manage Jenkins on the left and then Manage Plugins in the center.
Install the Blue Ocean plugin.
